race.description: Sportsbet Set A Deposit Limit Maiden Plate
race.comment: MAHALER (13) is a first-starter by Al Maher out of Roscrea Rose. Looked good winning her most recent trial. Looks set for a bright start to her career. CAUSEWELUVADELAIDE (8) resume and looks to have come on nicely during the break, owning to solid hitouts. Should blend into the race nicely from her middle draw and looks a huge threat. ONE WHIM (6) wound up strongly last time out to finish second over the 1000m at Port Lincoln. Will relish the rise in trip, though could find himself a long way back from the wide alley. Watch for him late. ILLUSTRATES (9) is mixing her form but has peaks that measure up. Will need plenty of luck from out there but is worth keeping safe under the light weight of the claim. LADY BIV (12) was a flashing light last time at huge odds. Trialled well in between runs and is worth keeping safe.
